        <section id="dogcaretips" aria-labelledby="tips-heading">
            <h2 id="tips-heading">Dog Care Tips</h2>
            <p>Taking care of your dog involves a mix of proper nutrition, regular health check-ups, grooming, exercise, and lots of love. Feed them high-quality food suited to their age and size, avoid toxic foods, and ensure they always have fresh water. Keep up with vet visits, vaccinations, and dental care to maintain their health. Regular brushing, bathing, and nail trimming will keep them clean and comfortable. Daily walks, playtime, and mental stimulation prevent boredom and keep them active. Create a safe home environment, free from hazards, and provide a cozy resting spot. Most importantly, shower them with affection, patience, and positive reinforcement to build a strong, happy bond. A well-cared-for dog is a joyful and loyal companion for life!</p>
        </section>
